<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 03:15:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国家开发银行航空部门采购80架空客A320neo喷气式飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-development-banks-aviation-unit-buys-80-airbus-a320neo-jets-2024-09-12/</link><description>国开金融租赁周四表示，将购买80架空客A320neo飞机，预计将于2030年开始交付。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 02:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-development-banks-aviation-unit-buys-80-airbus-a320neo-jets-2024-09-12/</guid></item><item><title>华尔街科技股推动亚洲股市上涨，美元兑日元延续涨势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-12/</link><description>亚洲股市周四反弹，追随华尔街科技股推动的涨势，而在美国核心通胀率小幅上扬以及美联储下周大​​幅降息的希望破灭后，美元保持涨势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 02:08:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称与中国就南海问题进行了“坦诚、坦诚”的会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-had-frank-candid-talks-with-china-south-china-sea-2024-09-12/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周四表示，菲律宾重申了其在南海萨比纳浅滩问题上的立场，尽管该国同意与中国探讨缓解该地区紧张局势的方法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 01:08:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-had-frank-candid-talks-with-china-south-china-sea-2024-09-12/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示美国企业对华乐观度跌至历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-businesses-optimism-china-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-09-12/</link><description>一项调查显示，政治紧张局势、中国经济增长放缓和激烈的国内竞争正在削弱美国企业对中国的信心，对五年前景的乐观情绪跌至历史最低点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 01:02:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-businesses-optimism-china-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-09-12/</guid></item><item><title>北京在多个地区争端中启动年度防务论坛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-kicks-off-annual-defence-forum-amid-multiple-regional-disputes-2024-09-12/</link><description>中国将于周四启动其最大规模的年度军事外交活动，在南海和台湾周边地区紧张局势不断升温的情况下，寻求扩大中国在全球南方的影响力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 00:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-kicks-off-annual-defence-forum-amid-multiple-regional-disputes-2024-09-12/</guid></item><item><title>Rho Motion 表示，尽管欧洲销量创 19 个月新低，但 8 月份全球电动汽车销量仍增长 20%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-20-august-despite-19-month-low-europe-rho-motion-says-2024-09-11/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 表示，受中国销量创历史新高的推动，8 月份全球纯电动和插电式混合动力汽车销量同比增长 20%，尽管欧洲销量下降 33%，为 2023 年 1 月以来最弱月份星期四。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 23:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-20-august-despite-19-month-low-europe-rho-motion-says-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>前中央情报局官员因为中国从事间谍活动被判入狱10年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ex-cia-officer-gets-10-years-prison-spying-china-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名前中央情报局官员在承认为中国从事间谍活动后于周三被判处 10 年监禁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ex-cia-officer-gets-10-years-prison-spying-china-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>视频游戏公司因“欺骗消费者”而受到欧盟投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/videogame-firms-hit-with-eu-complaint-over-tricking-consumers-2024-09-11/</link><description>周四，Epic Games、Electronic Arts、Roblox 和其他四家视频游戏公司遭到欧盟消费者投诉，指控他们误导游戏玩家花钱。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 22:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/videogame-firms-hit-with-eu-complaint-over-tricking-consumers-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：美国通胀拉锯后强势睁开眼睛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-11/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员敦促拜登堵住中国小包装进口的关税“漏洞”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-urge-biden-close-tariff-loophole-chinese-small-package-imports-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国众议院多数民主党议员周三敦促总统乔·拜登利用其行政权力，消除低价值包裹的关税“漏洞”，他们称这些包裹正被中国电子商务公司和芬太尼贩运者利用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 21:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-urge-biden-close-tariff-loophole-chinese-small-package-imports-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国查获350多个从中国进口枪支零部件的网站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-seizes-over-350-websites-used-import-gun-parts-china-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国当局周三表示，他们查获了 350 多个销售枪支消音器和来自中国的零部件的网站，这些零部件用于将半自动手枪改装成全自动机枪。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 20:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-seizes-over-350-websites-used-import-gun-parts-china-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国FDA向两家违反实验室规范的中国公司发出警告信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-fda-sends-warning-letters-two-chinese-firms-violating-lab-practices-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国食品和药物管理局周三向两家中国第三方检测公司发出警告信，理由是监管失误和动物护理违规行为，引发了人们对实验室生成数据的质量和完整性的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 18:36:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-fda-sends-warning-letters-two-chinese-firms-violating-lab-practices-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国贸易长官下周将在意大利举行贸易谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-trade-chief-set-talks-trade-italy-next-week-2024-09-11/</link><description>意大利政府消息人士周三表示，中国最高贸易官员将于下周抵达意大利进行会谈，北京方面正试图说服欧盟成员国拒绝欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的提议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 16:42:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-trade-chief-set-talks-trade-italy-next-week-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利为欧洲工厂寻找选址</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-scouting-locations-europe-plant-2024-09-11/</link><description>中国汽车制造商吉利汽车集团的高管在法兰克福接受路透社采访时表示，该公司正在欧洲寻找工厂选址，但尚未完全致力于建立本地生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:47:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-scouting-locations-europe-plant-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国和菲律宾就有争议的萨宾娜浅滩举行“坦诚”会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-hold-frank-talks-disputed-sabina-shoal-2024-09-11/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国外交部副部长和菲律宾副外长就海洋相关问题，特别是有争议的萨比纳浅滩问题进行了“坦诚、深入”的交流。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-hold-frank-talks-disputed-sabina-shoal-2024-09-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>